<div class='blog-posts-show-header__cover-column' style='background-image: url(https://uploads.republic.com/p/blog/posts/cover_photos/large_retina/000/000/093/93-1545142044-f24f19658840ed4fdd264dae35d125664f5cad9b.jpg)'></div>
